28
00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:39.660
mass.

29
00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.420
Cachexia or weight loss is

30
00:01:43.380 --> 00:01:46.940
very frequently the symptom that drives people to seek a doctor's help,

31
00:01:47.480 --> 00:01:51.100
and indeed, it often precedes a diagnosis of life-threatening cancer,

32
00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:53.840
as shown here in this very large study that

33
00:01:54.660 --> 00:01:58.460
weight loss of greater than 5% was highly associated with

34
00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:00.920
a diagnosis of a deadly disease.

35
00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:04.780
And cachexia, as I said, is a physical manifestation of a

36
00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:08.280
treatment-resistant state, chemotherapy reduction, surgical

37
00:02:08.361 --> 00:02:12.220
mortality, and importantly, immunotherapy response or

38
00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:16.580
