00:55:26.140 --> 00:55:29.700
The main form of kidney cancer is clear cell renal cell carcinoma,

943
00:55:30.020 --> 00:55:30.650
ccRCC.

944
00:55:31.910 --> 00:55:35.800
And in around 85% of

945
00:55:35.840 --> 00:55:39.640
the ccRCC cases, there is one driver

