00:56:54.760 --> 00:56:55.100
for

968
00:56:56.900 --> 00:56:59.500
genes involved in angiogenesis and proliferation.

969
00:57:00.780 --> 00:57:04.060
There is a specific molecule, allosteric inhibitor, called

